# UI Components Module

## PURPOSE
Reusable UI components used across different pages.
Promotes consistency and reduces code duplication.

## CONTAINS
- SubscriptionCard.js: Individual subscription display card
- Button.js: Reusable button component
- Loader.js: Loading spinner component
- ErrorMessage.js: Error display component
- PaymentModal.js: Payment prompt modal

## COMPONENT GUIDELINES
- Each component should be self-contained
- Accept props for customization
- Follow consistent styling
- Include proper accessibility attributes
- Handle edge cases (empty states, errors)

## REFERENCES
- Parent: /src/ui/.windsurf
- Root: /.windsurf
- Used by: /src/ui/popup/*

## RULES
- Components must be reusable
- No hardcoded data
- Proper event handling
- Responsive design
